---
title: "US37 — Personalised AI plan suggestions"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Premium User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>TrainScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SuggestPlan (AI)
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>AiGateway → Edge Function
  A->>B: tap "Suggest plan"
  B->>C: suggestPlan(goal, profile)
  C->>G: invoke suggest-plan
  G-->>C: plan draft
  alt accepted
    C-->>B: save fitness_plans + planned_workouts
    B-->>A: personalised plan active
  else regenerate
    B->>C: suggest again
  end
